  "text": "PERK then oligomerises and auto-phosphorylates to become active, and can transphosphorylate the translation initiation factor eIF2α [CITATION_1] and the basic leucine zipper (bZIP) transcription factor NF-E2-related factor 2 (Nrf2) [CITATION_2] .",
